{"id":833,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":833,"title":"Ezekiel 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","The judgment of Jerusalem will include famine, pestilence, war, and the scattering of her inhabitants."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.1","order":"02.27.005.55221"},["b","1"],"And thou, son of man, take thee a sharp knife, take thee a barber’s razor, and cause",["i","it"],"to pass upon thine head and upon thy beard: then take thee balances to weigh, and divide the",["i","hair."]],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.2","order":"02.27.005.55222"},["b","2"],"Thou shalt burn with fire a third part in the midst of the city, when the days of the siege are fulfilled: and thou shalt take a third part,",["i","and"],"smite about it with a knife: and a third part thou shalt scatter in the wind; and I will draw out a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"sword"],"after them."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.3","order":"02.27.005.55223"},["b","3"],"Thou shalt also take thereof a few in number, and bind them in thy skirts."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.4","order":"02.27.005.55224"},["b","4"],"Then take of them again, and cast them into the midst of the fire, and burn them in the fire;",["i","for"],"thereof shall a fire come forth into all the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.5","order":"02.27.005.55225"},["b","5"],"¶Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; This",["i","is"],"Jerusalem: I have set it in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"midst"],"of the nations and countries",["i","that are"],"round about her."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.6","order":"02.27.005.55226"},["b","6"],"And she hath changed my judgments into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"wickedness"],"more than the nations, and my statutes more than the countries that",["i","are"],"round about her: for they have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"refused"],"my judgments and my statutes, they have not walked in them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.7","order":"02.27.005.55227"},["b","7"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Because ye multiplied more than the nations that",["i","are"],"round about you,",["i","and"],"have not walked in my statutes, neither have kept my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"judgments"],", neither have done according to the judgments of the nations that",["i","are"],"round about you;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.8","order":"02.27.005.55228"},["b","8"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Behold, I, even I,",["i","am"],"against thee, and will execute judgments in the midst of thee in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"sight"],"of the nations."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.9","order":"02.27.005.55229"},["b","9"],"And I will do in thee that which I have not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"done"],", and whereunto I will not do any more the like, because of all thine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"abominations"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.10","order":"02.27.005.55230"},["b","10"],"Therefore the fathers shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"eat"],"the sons in the midst of thee, and the sons shall eat their fathers; and I will execute judgments in thee, and the whole remnant of thee will I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"scatter"],"into all the winds."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11","order":"02.27.005.55231"},["b","11"],"Wherefore,",["i","as"],"I live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Surely, because thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"defiled"],"my sanctuary with all thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"detestable"],"things, and with all thine abominations, therefore will I also",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"diminish"],["i","thee;"],"neither shall mine eye",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"spare"],", neither will I have any pity."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.12","order":"02.27.005.55232"},["b","12"],"¶A third part of thee shall die with the pestilence, and with famine shall they be consumed in the midst of thee: and a third part shall fall by the sword round about thee; and I will scatter a third part into all the winds, and I will draw out a sword after them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.13","order":"02.27.005.55233"},["b","13"],"Thus shall mine anger be accomplished, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"I"],"will cause my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"fury"],"to rest upon them, and I will be comforted: and they shall know that I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"spoken"],["i","it"],"in my zeal, when I have accomplished my fury in them."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.14","order":"02.27.005.55234"},["b","14"],"Moreover I will make thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"waste"],", and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"reproach"],"among the nations that",["i","are"],"round about thee, in the sight of all that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"pass"],"by."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.15","order":"02.27.005.55235"},["b","15"],"So it shall be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"reproach"],"and a taunt, an instruction and an astonishment unto the nations that",["i","are"],"round about thee, when I shall execute judgments in thee in anger and in fury and in furious rebukes. I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have spoken",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.16","order":"02.27.005.55236"},["b","16"],"When I shall send upon them the evil arrows of famine, which shall be for",["i","their"],"destruction,",["i","and"],"which I will send to destroy you: and I will increase the famine upon you, and will break your staff of bread:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.17","order":"02.27.005.55237"},["b","17"],"So will I send upon you famine and evil beasts, and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"bereave thee"],"; and pestilence and blood shall pass through thee; and I will bring the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"sword"],"upon thee. I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have spoken",["i","it."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.2a","order":"02.27.005.55238"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/12.14"},"Ezek. 12:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.5a","order":"02.27.005.55240"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/21.6"},"1 Ne. 21:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/4.11"},"Alma 4:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/39.11"},"39:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.9.8-9"},"D&C 103:9 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.6a","order":"02.27.005.55242"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/24.30"},"Alma 24:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.6b","order":"02.27.005.55244"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.19.18-20"},"1 Ne. 1:19 (18–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.13"},"2:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/7.14"},"7:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.7a","order":"02.27.005.55246"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/11.12"},"Ezek. 11:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.8a","order":"02.27.005.55248"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.91"},"D&C 42:91"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.9a","order":"02.27.005.55250"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.12"},"Dan. 9:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.9b","order":"02.27.005.55252"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.21"},"D&C 29:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.10a","order":"02.27.005.55254"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9"},"Jer. 19:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.20"},"Lam. 2:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.10b","order":"02.27.005.55256"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11a","order":"02.27.005.55258"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11b","order":"02.27.005.55260"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11c","order":"02.27.005.55262"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.19.18-20"},"Deut. 8:19 (18–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11d","order":"02.27.005.55264"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.4"},"Ezek. 7:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.17"},"20:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.13a","order":"02.27.005.55266"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.13.13-14"},"Ezek. 24:13 (13–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.13b","order":"02.27.005.55268"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.17"},"Ezek. 21:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.18"},"38:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.13c","order":"02.27.005.55270"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.36"},"D&C 20:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.14a","order":"02.27.005.55272"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.31"},"Lev. 26:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/2.17"},"Neh. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.14b","order":"02.27.005.55274"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.4"},"Ezek. 22:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.14c","order":"02.27.005.55276"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15"},"Lam. 2:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.15a","order":"02.27.005.55278"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/24.9"},"Jer. 24:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.17a","order":"02.27.005.55280"},["b","17a"],["span.small","IE"],"deprive of children.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.13.8-15"},"Ezek. 36:13 (8–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.17b","order":"02.27.005.55282"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.21"},"Ezek. 14:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.27"},"33:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.8"},"Rev. 6:8"],"."]]}
